# http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/OMO_0002000
<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/OMO_0002000> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#AnnotationProperty> .
<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/OMO_0002000> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000112> "'part disjoint with' 'defined by construct' \"\"\"\n    PREFIX owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#>\n    PREFIX : <http://example.org/\n    CONSTRUCT {\n      [\n        a owl:Restriction ;\n        owl:onProperty :part_of ;\n        owl:someValuesFrom ?a ;\n        owl:disjointWith [\n          a owl:Restriction ;\n          owl:onProperty :part_of ;\n          owl:someValuesFrom ?b\n        ]\n      ]\n    }\n    WHERE {\n      ?a :part_disjoint_with ?b .\n    }" .
<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/OMO_0002000> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> "Links an annotation property to a SPARQL CONSTRUCT query which is meant to provide semantics for a shortcut relation." .
<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/OMO_0002000> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "defined by construct" .
