<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000196> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000020> .
<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000196> <http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/identifier> "053-BFO" .
<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000196> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "bearer of"@en .
<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000196> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "b bearer of c =Def c inheres in b"@en .
<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000196> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#example> "A patch of ink is the bearer of a colour quality; an organism is the bearer of a temperature quality"@en .
