<https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/NFDI_0000226> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/NFDI_0000226> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "is subject of"@en .
<https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/NFDI_0000226> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel> "is described by" .
