# 
# https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000077
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000077> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000077> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "specified by value"@en .
