<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/OBI_0001937> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/OBI_0002135> .
<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/OBI_0001937> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/OBI_0001933> .
<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/OBI_0001937> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#real> .
