<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/OBI_0001937> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000116> "A range of 'real' might be better than 'float'. For now we follow 'has measurement value' until we can consider technical issues with SPARQL queries and reasoning." .
