<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/OBI_0002135> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/OBI_0001933> .
<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/OBI_0002135> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> "A relation between a value specification and a literal."@en .
<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/OBI_0002135> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000116> "This is not an RDF/OWL object property. It is intended to link a value found in e.g. a database column of 'M' (the literal) to an instance of a value specification class, which can then be linked to indicate that this is about the biological gender of a human subject." .
<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/OBI_0002135> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000119> "OBI" .
<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/OBI_0002135> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "has specified value"@en .
