# 
# http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/COB_0000082
<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/COB_0000082> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/COB_0000082> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000015> .
<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/COB_0000082> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> "A process that is initiated by an agent who intends to carry out a plan to achieve an objective through one or more actions as described in a plan specification."@en .
