<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000109> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000112> "Examples of measurement data are the recoding of the weight of a mouse as {40,mass,\"grams\"}, the recording of an observation of the behavior of the mouse {,process,\"agitated\"}, the recording of the expression level of a gene as measured through the process of microarray experiment {3.4,luminosity,}."@en .
<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000109> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> "A measurement datum is an information content entity that is a recording of the output of a measurement such as produced by a device."@en .
<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000109> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000116> "2/2/2009 is_specified_output of some assay?"@en .
<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000109> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000119> "OBI_0000305"@en .
<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000109> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000119> "group:OBI"@en .
<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000109> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "measurement datum"@en .
