<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000577> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000112> "The sentence \"The article has Pubmed ID 12345.\" contains a CRID that has two parts: one part is the CRID symbol, which is '12345'; the other part denotes the CRID registry, which is Pubmed."@en .
<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000577> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> "A symbol that is part of a CRID and that is sufficient to look up a record from the CRID's registry."@en .
