<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000579> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0020020> .
<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000579> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000112> "PubMed is a CRID registry. It has a code set of PubMed identifiers associated with journal articles. "@en .
<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000579> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> "A code set of CRID records, each consisting of a CRID symbol and additional information which was recorded in the code set through an assigning a centrally registered identifier process."@en .
<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000579> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000118> "CRID registry" .
<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000579> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000119> "Original proposal from Bjoern, discussions at IAO calls"@en .
<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000579> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "centrally registered identifier registry"@en .
