_:genid183 <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
_:genid183 <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#intersectionOf> _:genid186 .
_:genid186 <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#rest> _:genid184 .
_:genid184 <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#rest> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#nil> .
_:genid184 <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#first> _:genid185 .
_:genid185 <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#someValuesFrom> <https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/NFDI_0000229> .
_:genid185 <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#onProperty> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/RO_0000087> .
