<http://purls.helmholtz-metadaten.de/mwo/MWO_0001012> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "date process ended"@en .
<http://purls.helmholtz-metadaten.de/mwo/MWO_0001012> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "The date and time at which the experimental process was completed." .
