<http://purls.helmholtz-metadaten.de/mwo/MWO_0001065> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "license holder role"@en .
<http://purls.helmholtz-metadaten.de/mwo/MWO_0001065> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "License holder role is an agent role that is realized through holding or exercising rights granted by a license." .
