<https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/NFDI_0000011> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "A realizable entity that represents a structured set of intended actions or steps designed to achieve specific objectives or outcomes."@en .
