<https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/NFDI_0001009> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "GND identifier"@en .
<https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/NFDI_0001009> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "A centrally registered identifier that is issued by the German National Library. The Integrated Authority File (GND) is facilitates the collaborative use and administration of authority data. These authority data represent and describe entities, i.e. persons, corporate bodies, conferences and events, geographic entities, topics and works relating to cultural and academic collections."@en .
