<https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/NFDI_0001010> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "The centrally registered identifier VIAF (Virtual International Authority File) is an international authority file that links and integrates authority records from multiple national libraries and other organizations. It provides a unique identifier for authors, creators, and entities, facilitating better data sharing and cataloging across institutions."@en .
<https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/NFDI_0001010> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#example> "https://viaf.org/en/viaf/137346469" .
