<https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/NFDI_0001011> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "GeoNames is a geographical database that provides information on places, including names, coordinates, and administrative divisions. It integrates data from multiple sources and is widely used for geolocation, mapping, and geographic information systems (GIS)."@en .
<https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/NFDI_0001011> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#example> "https://www.geonames.org/2950159" .
