<https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/NFDI_0001015> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "FactGrid is a collaborative, structured knowledge database designed for historical research. It operates on Wikibase and focuses on documenting historical entities, events, and relationships."@en .
