<https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/NFDI_0001055> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "The TGN Identifier refers to a unique ID within the Getty Thesaurus of Geographic Names (TGN), which is a controlled vocabulary developed to standardize geographic names for use in cultural heritage and library contexts. The TGN is part of the Getty Vocabulary Program by the Getty Research Institute."@en .
