<https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/NFDI_0001057> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/NFDI_0001057> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/NFDI_0000229> .
<https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/NFDI_0001057> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "co organizer role"@en .
