<https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/NFDI_0001058> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "A role inherent in an agent that is realized when shareing the responsibilities of representing an organization, group, or initiative, typically communicating its views, policies, or findings to the public."@en .
# 
# https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/NFDI_0001059
<https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/NFDI_0001059> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
