<https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/NFDI_0001059> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "collaboration partner role"@en .
<https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/NFDI_0001059> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "A role inherent in an agent that is realized when engageing in cooperative work with another individual or organization toward a shared goal, such as research, development, or business initiatives."@en .
# 
