<https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/NFDI_0001060> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "manufacturer role"@en .
<https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/NFDI_0001060> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "A role inherent in an agent that is realized when being responsible for producing goods, components, or materials through industrial or commercial processes."@en .
<https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/NFDI_0001060> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#example> "Siemens as a manufacturer of industrial automation equipment or Intel as a manufacturer of semiconductor chips" .
