# https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/NFDI_0001101
<https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/NFDI_0001101> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/NFDI_0001101> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000300> .
<https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/NFDI_0001101> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "added value textual entity"@en .
<https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/NFDI_0001101> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "An added value textual entity is a textual entity that describes the achievements, benefits, or additional value generated by a project, service, or initiative, highlighting its impact, improvements, or contributions." .
<https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/NFDI_0001101> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#editorialNote> "In responce to competency questions like what are the added values of project X1 or service X2." .
