<https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/NFDI_0001105> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "A Conference Paper is a scholarly publication that presents research findings at an academic or professional conference, typically published in conference proceedings." .
