<https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/NFDI_0001209> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#seeAlso> "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000013" .
<https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/NFDI_0001209> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "A Journal Article is a peer-reviewed scholarly publication that presents original research, review studies, or theoretical discussions, typically published in academic journals." .
<https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/NFDI_0001209> <https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/NFDI_0010013> "https://github.com/ISE-FIZKarlsruhe/nfdicore/issues/119" .
