<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0020099> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "bravais lattice (3D)"@en .
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0020099> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "The bravais lattice is a categorical value specification that specifies value of the crystal structure quality. It describes the possible geometric arrangement of lattice points in a crystal. The present descriptor is limited to the 14 possible three-dimensional arrangements."@en .
