<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0025001> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000116> "There's a dfference between composition and chemical compositon for the following reason: chemical compositon is relevant when the mass/volume/mole proportions of chemical elements(!) are identified, whlist composition includes proportions of molecules, other pure chemical substances, or even proptions of objects (in an object aggregate)."@en .
