<http://purls.helmholtz-metadaten.de/mwo/MWO_0001017> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "A NFDI MatWerk organization that contributes domain-specific research and expertise, integrating real-world scientific challenges to validate and enhance the infrastructure." .
<http://purls.helmholtz-metadaten.de/mwo/MWO_0001017> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isDefinedBy> "https://nfdi-matwerk.de/project/structure" .
