<http://purls.helmholtz-metadaten.de/mwo/MWO_0001018> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "A NFDI MatWerk organization that demonstrates how the developed infrastructure can be applied to solve practical research problems, ensuring usability and impact." .
