<https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/NFDI_0001072> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "Doctor (PhD or equivalent academic doctorate)" .
# 
# https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/NFDI_0001073
<https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/NFDI_0001073> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#NamedIndividual> .
