<https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/NFDI_0001073> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "Doctor of Engineering (German doctorate in engineering)." .
# 
# https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/NFDI_0001074
<https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/NFDI_0001074> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#NamedIndividual> .
<https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/NFDI_0001074> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/NFDI_0001056> .
<https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/NFDI_0001074> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "finished status"@en .
<https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/NFDI_0001074> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "Finished Status is a status specification that indicates an entity, process, or project has successfully reached its intended goal and is considered complete." .
# 
# https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/NFDI_0001075
<https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/NFDI_0001075> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#NamedIndividual> .
<https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/NFDI_0001075> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/NFDI_0001050> .
<https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/NFDI_0001075> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "hybrid implementation"@en .
<https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/NFDI_0001075> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "Hybrid Implementation is an event implementation specification that defines the organization of an event that integrates both physical (on-site) and virtual (online) participation modes" .
# 
# https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/NFDI_0001076
<https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/NFDI_0001076> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#NamedIndividual> .
<https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/NFDI_0001076> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/NFDI_0001052> .
<https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/NFDI_0001076> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "internal access"@en .
<https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/NFDI_0001076> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "Internal Access is an information access specification that defines policies and mechanisms restricting access to information exclusively within an organization, institution, or research group." .
# 
# https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/NFDI_0001077
<https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/NFDI_0001077> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#NamedIndividual> .
<https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/NFDI_0001077> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/NFDI_0001040> .
<https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/NFDI_0001077> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "M.Sc."@en .
<https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/NFDI_0001077> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "Master of Science (graduate degree in science/engineering)." .
# 
# https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/NFDI_0001078
<https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/NFDI_0001078> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#NamedIndividual> .
<https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/NFDI_0001078> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/NFDI_0001050> .
<https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/NFDI_0001078> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "on site implementation"@en .
<https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/NFDI_0001078> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "On-Site Implementation is an event implementation specification that defines the organization of an event that occurs exclusively at a physical location with in-person attendance." .
# 
# https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/NFDI_0001079
<https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/NFDI_0001079> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#NamedIndividual> .
<https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/NFDI_0001079> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/NFDI_0001050> .
<https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/NFDI_0001079> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "online implementation"@en .
<https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/NFDI_0001079> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "Online Implementation is an event implementation specification that defines the organization of an event conducted entirely through virtual platforms, enabling remote participation via digital communication technologies." .
# 
# https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/NFDI_0001080
<https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/NFDI_0001080> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#NamedIndividual> .
<https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/NFDI_0001080> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/NFDI_0001052> .
<https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/NFDI_0001080> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "open access"@en .
<https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/NFDI_0001080> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "Open Access is an information access specification that defines policies allowing unrestricted public access to information resources, ensuring free availability without subscription or payment barriers." .
# 
# https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/NFDI_0001081
<https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/NFDI_0001081> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#NamedIndividual> .
<https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/NFDI_0001081> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/NFDI_0001051> .
<https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/NFDI_0001081> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "organizational funding"@en .
<https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/NFDI_0001081> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "Organizational Funding is a funding specification that defines the financial structures, budgets, and resource allocation strategies for sustaining the operations of an organization or institution." .
# 
# https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/NFDI_0001082
<https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/NFDI_0001082> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#NamedIndividual> .
<https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/NFDI_0001082> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/NFDI_0001056> .
<https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/NFDI_0001082> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "paused status"@en .
<https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/NFDI_0001082> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "Paused Status is a status specification that indicates an entity, process, or project is temporarily halted but may resume at a later stage." .
# 
# https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/NFDI_0001083
<https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/NFDI_0001083> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#NamedIndividual> .
<https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/NFDI_0001083> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/NFDI_0001052> .
<https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/NFDI_0001083> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "paywall access"@en .
<https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/NFDI_0001083> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "Paywall Access is an information access specification that defines policies requiring users to purchase, subscribe, or obtain institutional licenses to access digital or physical information resources." .
# 
# https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/NFDI_0001084
<https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/NFDI_0001084> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#NamedIndividual> .
<https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/NFDI_0001084> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/NFDI_0001040> .
<https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/NFDI_0001084> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "PD. Dr."@en .
<https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/NFDI_0001084> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "Privatdozent (Dr. with habilitation, qualified to teach at a university)" .
# 
# https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/NFDI_0001085
<https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/NFDI_0001085> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#NamedIndividual> .
<https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/NFDI_0001085> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/NFDI_0001040> .
<https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/NFDI_0001085> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "PD. Dr. habil."@en .
<https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/NFDI_0001085> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "Privatdozent with Habilitation (higher academic qualification in Germany)" .
# 
# https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/NFDI_0001086
<https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/NFDI_0001086> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#NamedIndividual> .
<https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/NFDI_0001086> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/NFDI_0001056> .
<https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/NFDI_0001086> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "planning status"@en .
<https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/NFDI_0001086> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "Planning Status is a status specification that indicates an entity, process, or project is in a preparatory or strategic development phase before execution." .
# 
# https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/NFDI_0001087
<https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/NFDI_0001087> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#NamedIndividual> .
<https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/NFDI_0001087> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/NFDI_0001040> .
<https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/NFDI_0001087> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Prof."@en .
<https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/NFDI_0001087> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "Professor (academic title for a senior faculty member)." .
# 
# https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/NFDI_0001088
<https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/NFDI_0001088> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#NamedIndividual> .
<https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/NFDI_0001088> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/NFDI_0001040> .
<https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/NFDI_0001088> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Prof. Dr."@en .
<https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/NFDI_0001088> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "Professor with a doctorate." .
# 
# https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/NFDI_0001089
<https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/NFDI_0001089> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#NamedIndividual> .
<https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/NFDI_0001089> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/NFDI_0001040> .
<https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/NFDI_0001089> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Prof. Dr.-Ing."@en .
<https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/NFDI_0001089> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "Professor with a doctorate in engineering." .
# 
# https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/NFDI_0001090
<https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/NFDI_0001090> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#NamedIndividual> .
<https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/NFDI_0001090> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/NFDI_0001051> .
<https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/NFDI_0001090> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "project funding"@en .
<https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/NFDI_0001090> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "Project Funding is a funding specification that defines the financial mechanisms, grants, and investment strategies used to support specific research, development, or innovation projects." .
# 
# https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/NFDI_0001091
<https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/NFDI_0001091> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#NamedIndividual> .
<https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/NFDI_0001091> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/NFDI_0001052> .
<https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/NFDI_0001091> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "restricted access"@en .
<https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/NFDI_0001091> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "Restricted Access is an information access specification that defines policies limiting access to specific users, organizations, or groups based on predefined criteria such as confidentiality, security, or legal regulations." .
# 
# https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/NFDI_0001092
<https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/NFDI_0001092> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#NamedIndividual> .
